	* modules/system/syskeys/: syskeys.class.php, syskeys.class.php:
	#1883 - fixed - added a check, which doesn't allow an empty key
	type.

2007-02-14 02:14  merlinyoda

	* modules/tasks/do_task_aed.php: Fixed bug introduced by previous
	fix to #1695. Task parent was always being set to task's own id and
	making it a "root level" task.
	
	Only existance of $_POST['new_task_project'] was checked and that
	value was not 0 but did not check that project actually changed. 
	(that curreent project was different than new project).

2007-02-14 02:13  merlinyoda

	* modules/tasks/do_task_aed.php: 
	Fixed bug introduced by previous fix to #1695. Task parent was
	always being set to task's own id and making it a "root level"
	task.
	
	Only existance of $_POST['new_task_project'] was checked and that
	value was not 0 but did not check that project actually changed. 
	(that curreent project was different than new project).

