2007-01-28 13:19  ajdonnison

	* classes/ui.class.php: Removed template creation from the
	constructor as it gets corrupted on saving to session and
	re-initialising on wakeup.  Now creates the template class instance
	just prior to initialising it.	This fixes problems with smarty
	errors on missing functions, etc.

