2006-12-16 05:02  merlinyoda

	* lib/ezpdf/: class.ezpdf.php, class.pdf.php: 
	Got rid of the carrage return characters so they don't show up
	under *nix.
	
	Added the following lines to the stream() function in
	lib/ezpdf/class.pdf.php to solve the problem of certain versions IE
	trying to download/display a pdf report based on the page/arguments
	in the URL instead of what is passed to it in the HTTP header
	information (I've had a similiar problem in other programs because
	of IE's disreguard of web standards by running everything in
	"quirks" mode unless you explicitly specify otherwise not to):
	
	  header( "Pragma: ");
	  header( "Cache-Control: public");

