2006-11-12 16:35  caseydk

	* classes/dp.class.php, modules/projects/projects.class.php,
	modules/tasks/projects_tab.view.task_logs.php: very subtle
	combination of errors:	- if you had a user who was denied access
	to Companies as a whole, but then allowed access to one, you'd get
	an ambiguous company_id in the where clause;  - in order to correct
	this, the aliasing mechanism had to be tweaked to add the key when
	provided but also tweak a couple other queries where a prefix was
	referenced but not used;  - i've tested my modules locally and in
	my server and haven't found any further problems;

