2006-08-01 07:07  merlinyoda

	* modules/system/do_systemconfig_aed.php: 
	Added hidden form fields for "config_group" and "config_type"
	fields for system config page. Add/Edit page for system config
	takes new values from POST and assings them to the proper object
	variable to be stored.	Previous setup would "forget" these values
	and assign blank values into many of the database fields, causing a
	loss of needed information.
	
	Also fixed checkbox functionality on system config page. Value
	attributes for checkboxes were being set to their previous values
	instead of "true" when checked. Since POST data is only passed
	along by *checked* checkbox items, newly uncheck items remained
	unchanged (the values weren't posted to be updated) and newly
	checked items were passing their old value of "false" (old value
	passed to POST instead of "true", new value). Unchenged valued were
	unaffected.

2006-08-01 02:45  merlinyoda

	* modules/admin/vw_usr_sessions.php: 
	Another "Active Sessions" tweak. Correted Company "order by" link.

