2006-07-26 05:59  merlinyoda

	* classes/dp.class.php, modules/projects/projects.class.php,
	modules/tasks/listtasks.php, modules/tasks/tasks.class.php: Fixed
	Bug 1709: Added function "dPTrimAll" to main dP class. Only class
	variables of string types are trimmed. Trim function is called
	immediately before the modules respective "store" function.
	Exception is made in task module. The task log description field
	value is preserved and restored after the parent function is
	called.
	
	Also modified code under the task module to make the "Last Update"
	field and the highlighted status color more "accurate" by using the
	history module if present as opposed to the last task log. Noted
	need for "actual" end date  field for a given task in code.

