2006-07-07 22:16  merlinyoda

	* modules/tasks/tasks.php: Fixed Bug 1701: Table "user_tasks"
	needed to be prepended to $from instead of appended so that the
	result was "user_tasks, tasks" instead of "tasks, user_tasks". 
	This was messing up the following join statement as it was trying
	to join using wrong table.

2006-07-07 06:49  merlinyoda

	* db/dotproject.sql: 
	applying fixes for Bug #1713 and Bug # 1714 to HEAD Branch:
	
	Fixed Bug 1713: changed instances of "VALUES (''" and "VALUES
	(NULL" to "VALUES (0" for relevant columns (mainly for numeric ID
	column on "config" table)
	
	... minor code cosmetic changes also.  changed "INSERT INTO config
	" to "INSERT INTO `config`" for purposes of code regularity.
	
	Fixed trivial bug #1714:
	
	changed version number string from '2.0.2' to '2.0.4'

