	modules/system/addeditpref.php: - made tasks module rely more on
	the findImage function - updated smarty showImage to default height
	to width if only first is available - added setting for iconsets -
	added support for iconsets drop a directory in style/_iconsets the
	directory has the following structure
	/style/_iconsets/{$iconstyle}/ - files from /images/
	/style/_iconsets/{$iconstyle}/_icons/ - files from /images/icons/
	/style/_iconsets/{$iconstyle}/_obj/ - files from /images/obj/
	/style/_iconsets/{$iconstyle}/{$module}/ - files from
	/module/{$module}/images/

