	modules/projects/companies_tab.view.active_projects.php,
	modules/projects/companies_tab.view.archived_projects.php: I'm
	sorry there are so many changes bundled in one commit, but sf was
	down for a while ...  Mostly work on smartification and a few
	changes to how translation and auto tabs work to fascilitate it
	
	- made translations load all language files that are needed by
	automatically inserted modules as well - moved code in index.php
	for automatic module loading higher up in the file, so it's before
	translations are loaded (for the change above) - moved
	style/smarty1/companies/list.php to style/smarty1/projects/list.php
	- it was about projects rather than companies - created tabs in
	projects module for the companies module that describes the
	projects in a selected company (replacing the files vw_active and
	vw_archived in companies) - created translation values for company
	and project fields (company_name, company_type etc) used by
	list.php (in both companies and projects) - created a subclass of
	Smarty called CTemplate. Made it a variable of AppUI.  - renamed
	the global $smarty to $tpl - the CTemplate and $tpl changes were
	done to make it possible to replace Smarty with a different
	template engine if needed at a later date - CTitleBlock class
	converted to use smarty
	
	---more work in progress

