	Please note, header translations are not done/handled yet.  Please
	note even more - the style/smarty1/companies/list.html file shows
	how lists can be handled - both displaying array of data and more
	importantly laying down the grounds for custom order of fields!
	Please if you do any work on smartification on list type of pages,
	use this or similar format, so custom order will be a breeze after
	that. (I hope people read these :).

2005-07-21 00:02  cyberhorse

