2005-07-20 23:28  cyberhorse

	* classes/ui.class.php, lib/smarty/Smarty.class.php,
	lib/smarty/plugins/function.dParraySelect.php,
	lib/smarty/plugins/function.dPformSafe.php,
	lib/smarty/plugins/function.dPtranslate.php,
	modules/companies/addedit.php: WARNING: From this change on, CVS is
	to be considered unstable ... sorry guys but this has to be done,
	and sooner rather than later.
	
	Now for the change - smarty going in.  dp functions to handle html,
	wrapped up in smarty functions (later to be replaced with pure
	smarty functions).  Converted functions so far - arraySelect(),
	dPformSafe() and $AppUI->_()
	
	The only file converted in smarty so far is
	modules/companies/addedit.php (and the resulting
	style/smarty1/companies/addedit.html template) but for that change,
	a lot of the ground work (I believe) has been made. To help with
	smartification, use the $smarty variable already declared, and put
	theme files in directories, named after the module/file they relate
	to in smarty1.

