2005-05-19 17:11  ajdonnison

	* modules/tasks/viewgantt.php, includes/db_connect.php,
	modules/projects/viewgantt.php: Moved memory limit setting into
	db_connect to ensure that it is always set, and set early enough
	that it takes effect (some Apache2 installations were reporting the
	setting having no effect, this was fixed by setting it earlier).
	Also removed the php_restore as the original value is always
	restored when the script terminates anyway.

