	everything its done from dPgetConfig - Changed all user first and
	last name queries to contact first and last name - Dropped some
	temporary tables to avoid SQL errors - I need to debug all system
	in order to solve conflicts generated mainly by the user=>contact
	issue

2004-10-22 07:25  ajdonnison

	* db/: dotproject.sql, upgrade_latest.sql: Added missing fields for
	files table.  Added all missing tables to upgrade script.

2004-10-22 01:22  jcgonz

	* includes/db_adodb.php: The upgrade_latest script is not prepared
	to be executed each time an SQL error occurs. It deletes
	information, duplicates some more. It's a very good idea to have an
	auto-update feature, we need to work on an idea how to solve these
	issues.

2004-10-20 04:44  jcgonz

	* includes/config-dist.php: Changed default minimum login and
	password lenght to 4 characters.  It was contradictorious, admin is
	less that 7 characters length.

2004-10-20 04:40  jcgonz

	* db/dotproject.sql: There was a simple syntax error withing the
	sql creation statement

