	* modules/projects/projects.class.php: couldn't create projects
	anymore without fixing this. Somebody had assumed all projects have
	departments and contacts. Something very strange here - this code
	was over 3 months old, but had some serious problems, like
	assigning project_id to non-existant task_id fields in some table
	etc. Why wasn't it giving errors before?!

