	* index.php: Added a check for the $_SESSION['all_tabs'] array and
	ensured the array linkage to session is the same way around as the
	later usage.  For some reason without doing this some systems seem
	to generate phantom array pointers with $all_tabs[0] pointing to
	$all_tabs, etc.

