2004-08-24 08:47  jcgonz

	* modules/admin/vw_usr_log.php: In order to enable admin to see
	individual access reports

2004-08-24 08:45  jcgonz

	* index.php: Solved another session issue.  Actually I discovered
	that the history module and the access log registry are doing more
	or less the same thing. The only substantial difference is that the
	access log registry is built in the users module and it calculates
	the idle time. Those calcultations are shown within the user lists
	and within the user details.

