2004-05-01 04:10  bloaterpaste

	* db/dotproject.sql, modules/projects/addedit.php,
	modules/projects/do_project_aed.php,
	modules/projects/projects.class.php, modules/projects/view.php:
	Adding project_departments and project_contacts fields to the
	projects table to support department and contact association with 
	projects.  This isn't the right way to implement this association,
	but it's the way that's currently used in tasks, so should be fine
	for now.  At some point, we should build seperate db table for
	handle this association, like the task->user association is
	currently handled.
	
	Added UI support for selection and display of contact and
	department information.

