	* ChangeLog: ChangeLog update

2004-01-11 15:23  ajdonnison

	* index.php, classes/ui.class.php, includes/version.php,
	style/classic/header.php, style/default/header.php,
	style/default/login.php: Removed version from index.php and into
	includes/version.php.  Changed ui.class to provide getVersion
	function.  Changed all calls to getConfig('version') to
	getVersion()

2004-01-11 15:12  ajdonnison

	* includes/: config-dist.php, version.php: Added external version
	file to centralise and simplify version management.

2004-01-11 14:34  ajdonnison

	* db/dotproject_102.sql: Changes made by jcgonz originally to
	dotproject_101.sql, now migrated.
	
	Now users are able to relate tasks to contacts from the project's
	owner company. Useful for CRM functionality.
	
	Companies can now have custom fields too!
	
	Custom fields in tasks can now be created. A record with serialized
	data must be added to the sysvals table like:
	TaskCustomFields->0|a:3:{s:4:"name";s:12:"Quote
	number";s:4:"type";s:4:"text";s:7:"options";s:24:"maxlength="12"
	size="10"";} A new text box will be displayed for input with the
	leyend quote number in the tasks module.
	
	Companies and Contacts are now linked by the company name (in
	text).	They are not linked by ID so that contacts don't have to
	have companies registered in the Companies section so it maintains
	backwards compatibility.  New department field added please check
	the upgrade SQL file. Department can be linked to the Company
	department by text also.  Dotproject now has some mini CRM
	features!
	
	Now users can relate departments to tasks.

