2003-02-15 06:41  kobudo

	* includes/config-dist.php: John creates a "config-dist.php" file
	to replace our config.php file.
	
	This will help reduce opportunity for overwriting config.php files
	on dotproject upgrades, and make it easier for our development team
	to checkout dotproject (and check in) without killing local
	connections.

